00:57:25.547 --> 00:57:34.590
I turn my back on the world. I turn my back on my sin. And from this day forward, Lord, I'm born again.

00:57:34.591 --> 00:57:41.756
I'll serve you with all my heart. Make it a clean start for me.

00:57:41.757 --> 00:57:49.919
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. I dedicate my heart to you. I dedicate my life to you.

00:57:49.920 --> 00:57:57.039
Thank you, Lord, that you're making everything new and you're giving me another chance.

00:57:57.040 --> 00:58:07.988
Jesus, I'll serve you from this day forward and I'll do the best I can as I dedicate my life to you in the name of Jesus.

00:58:07.989 --> 00:58:18.576
Amen and amen.'I believe if you just said that prayer, you just gave your heart to Jesus Christ. I believe that, behold, all things are made new today.

00:58:18.577 --> 00:58:27.404
You may have been a real knucklehead or whatever, but I believe that from this day forward, he's made everything new.

00:58:27.405 --> 00:58:34.484
As far as the east is from the west, he's taken your sins from you and cast them into the sea of forgetfulness.

00:58:34.485 --> 00:58:38.935
He'll never remember them anymore; he said it's washed, it's gone.

00:58:38.936 --> 00:58:47.513
And now, if the devil tries to remind you of your past, remind him of his future because he'll come and try to mess with you.

00:58:47.514 --> 00:58:59.768
But the Bible says, 'Submit yourself therefore unto God. Resist the devil and he will flee.'That's what it said and I believe it.

00:58:59.769 --> 00:59:09.196
He tries to mess with me and I say, 'Get out of here in Jesus'name!

00:59:09.197 --> 00:59:20.239
You're not tormenting me!'I've had two visitations from the devil face to face. One of them was really wild.

00:59:20.240 --> 00:59:27.118
But I want to tell you, every single time he's defeated by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of my testimony.

00:59:27.119 --> 00:59:35.148
Jesus Christ paid the price for me to have authority over the devil, and you have authority over the devil too.

00:59:35.149 --> 00:59:50.520
So what do you do now? You go to a Bible-believing church. You come here and pray with us; come and be a part of our little church community.

00:59:50.521 --> 00:59:55.613
I appreciate all y'all coming and praying with us every night and praying for our nation.

00:59:55.614 --> 01:00:00.954
So start getting plugged into a Bible-believing church. I would go to a non-denominational church.

01:00:00.955 --> 01:00:06.278
Go there, tell the pastor, 'I need to be water-baptized.'Get water-baptized.

01:00:06.279 --> 01:00:14.719
Read your Bible. Pray every day. And that's part of the Christian life—you walk it out. Tell people about the decision you made today.

01:00:14.720 --> 01:00:23.421
Tell them, 'I got born again watching some bald-headed guy on YouTube.'And I'm telling you, the best is yet to come for you.

01:00:23.422 --> 01:00:33.150
I believe from this time forward, even by this time next year, if you keep on this and get that word down inside of you, it'll change you from the inside out.

01:00:33.151 --> 01:00:39.039
I just want to encourage you: don't give up. Jesus never gave up on you.

01:00:39.040 --> 01:00:44.051
He's always there; he's an ever-present help in a time of need. And he loves you.

